description: The fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of its assets (exclusive of collateral held from securities lending) in the securities included in the index. The index utilizes a proprietary, quantitative methodology developed by the index provider, designed to identify companies that have a risk of being disrupted and as a result could underperform their relevant sector.
name: GraniteShares XOUT U.S. Large Cap ETF
